API Class 3:

RestAssured - java based library to automate Rest APIs

JSON - file that contains data that need to be exchanged 

[ --> array
	{ -ct-> obje
		"id": "345",
		"firstName": "John"	
	}

	{
		"id": "346",
		"firstName": "Jane"
	}
]


Request: 
	Parameters: 
		path(/) --> continue of your endpoint using
		query(?) --> comes after your path parameter Key=value (? page=2) to filter
	Headers:
	Body:

Response: 
	Status
	Headers
	Body

Status code:
200 - OK
201 - Created
400 -  Bad Request
404 - Not Found
500 - Internal Server Error

This is URI:
https://got-quotes.herokuapp.com/quotes?char=tyrion

This is URL:
https://got-quotes.herokuapp.com/quotes

